desc: 파사의 힘을 지닌 특수한 귀석. 왕후귀족의 장식품으로 사용되는 경우가 많다

dictionary.lore: A precious stone with hidden evil powers, which is often used in decorations worn by royalty. However it is very difficult to process and it is said that only the most skilled craftsman can draw out its true power. It was found written in a newly discovered book that, though they don't exist in Elgaia, some have been produced in Cordelica.

name: 파사석
